{"tid":1564320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鴨脷洲賞月唱歌賀中秋","createTime":"2019-09-12T17:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T19:46:40.000Z","uid":14100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6adecfe5d6b2ee68530438a2282da428b4b8d5b8","tid":1564320,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"組團聽晚去唱歌,唱完自由活動～中秋節千祈唔好玩得咁癲丫～～<br />\n<br />\n時間：22：00<br />\n地點：鴨脷洲<br />\n活動目的： 中秋唱歌仲洗教？當然仲有玩蠟燭，鐘意嘅許下願都得～例如五大訴求之類<br />\n<br />\n不過大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span>去<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">利澤樓c3 1837室</span></span>喎！！<br />\n         <br />\n點解？因為果到會有人渣掉鏹水架！（好似係）        <br />\n<br />\n不過中秋節，玩下d螢光棒，玩下蠟燭都好正常啫係咪？？"},{"pid":"243efb22685c538e0d1109d8d5f2dc4afe781c54","tid":1564320,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%